<para style="p">For the chief musician; on a stringed instrument. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Hear my cry, God;</para>

<para style="q1">attend to my prayer.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />From the ends of the earth will I call to you when my heart is overwhelmed;</para>

<para style="q1">lead me to the rock that is higher than I.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For you have been a refuge for me,</para>

<para style="q1">a strong tower from the enemy.</para>
